NK020(wa)006:0: de la so so'i dam rgya 'ching tshul ni /
NK020(wa)006:1: rdo rje bsdams ba gzhi rab bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)006:3: gung mo myu gu ltar mnyam par sgreng la /
NK020(wa)006:4: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ra h+aum /
NK020(wa)006:6: gung mo nang du gshibs nas sbas pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:9: gung mo rin chen 'dra ba'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:12: gung mo pad+ma ltar dgug pa la /
NK020(wa)006:15: rdor bsdams zlum po las mdzub mo bkug pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:18: rdor bsdams las gung mo gshibs te sgreng zhing mthe bong dam mathe'u chung bzhi phral nas sgreng la /
NK020(wa)006:21: mdzub gnyis lcags kyu ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)006:24: mdzub gnyis lto sbyar nas brkyang la /
NK020(wa)006:27: mtheb mdzub kyi se gol snying gar rdeb pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:30: mthe bong gshibs shing mdzub rtse sprad pa las tshigs bcag la /
NK020(wa)006:33: rdo rje thal mo las mtheb mdzub sngar ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)006:34: badz+ra te dzah rdo rje rgyal mtshan la /
NK020(wa)006:35: rdor bsdams las srin lag mathe'u chung gnyis mnyam par gshibs la /
NK020(wa)006:38: de nyid bskor nas kha'i phyogs bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:41: mthe bong mnyam gshibs mdzub rtse gnyis bkug la /
NK020(wa)006:44: gung mo gshibs te sgreng ba'i rtse bkug la /
NK020(wa)006:47: de las srin lag dang mathe'u chung gshibs la /
NK020(wa)006:50: rdor bsdams las mthe bong gnyis phan tshun du phye la thal mo bkan te kha'i phyogs bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:53: rdor bsdams las mthe bong mathe'u chung rtse sprad de bkye la /
NK020(wa)006:56: de las mdzub mo gshibs te snying gar brkyang la /
NK020(wa)006:59: mdzub gnyis bkug la lcags kyu ltar byas shing mthe chung gnyis gshibs pa mche ba ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)006:62: mathe'u chung gnyis kyi nang du mthe bong bcug pa'i rtsa ba mdzub mo gnyis kyis 'tshir la /
NK020(wa)006:65: rdor bsdams kyi mthe bong mnyam pa snying gar bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:71: rdor thal sbyar te kha nas dbyung ba'i rgyal /
NK020(wa)006:74: rdor thal bskor ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:77: rdor bsdams bcings pa thur du blug pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:80: rdor thal phye nas gyen du 'thor la /
NK020(wa)006:83: rdor bsdams las mthe bong mnyam pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:86: rdor thal phye nas brkyang la /
NK020(wa)006:89: rdor bsdams las mdzub mo bkug la /
NK020(wa)006:92: rdor bsdams las mthe bong g.yas pa nang du bcug la mdun pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:95: mthe bong mdzub mo so sor rtse sprad pa gdu bu lta ba'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:98: rdo rje bcing ba las mdzub mo nang du bcug la mthe bong gnyis kyis bsdams la /
NK020(wa)006:101: rnam snang la byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)006:103: mi bskyod rin 'byung don grub gsum la lag g.yon
NK020(wa)006:104: nu ma g.yon pa'i thad du chos gos kyi grwa
NK020(wa)006:106: g.yas sa gnon sogs so so'i phyag chen bcas la /
NK020(wa)006:109: snang mtha' la mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)006:110: pad+ma a mi ta b+ha h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi h+aum +aah rdor sems la /
NK020(wa)006:111: lag g.yas rdo rje gsor tshul dang g.yon bsgying ba'i rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)006:114: lag gnyis lcags kyu 'dzin pa lta bu'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:120: mthe bo mdzub kyi se gol snying gar bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:123: khu tshur gnyis gshibs dpral bar bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:126: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis steng 'og tu sbyar ba snying gar bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:127: badz+ra te dzah rdo rje rgyal mtshan la /
NK020(wa)006:128: khu tshur g.yon par g.yas pa'i gru mo btsugs la /
NK020(wa)006:131: g.yas g.yon so phreng 'dzin tshul kha phyogs bskor la /
NK020(wa)006:134: g.yas pa'i mtheb mdzub kyis g.yon pa'i pad+ma kha 'byed pa ltar byed la /
NK020(wa)006:137: snying gar g.yon pa ral gri mdud pa ltar byed la /
NK020(wa)006:140: rdo rje khu tshur kha sbyar ba mgal me ltar bskor la /
NK020(wa)006:143: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis kha nas dbyung ba ltar byed la /
NK020(wa)006:146: rdo rje thal mo gar bskor bkrol nas 'gram g.yas g.yon dang spyi bor bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:149: go cha bkon tshul gyi rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:152: khu tshur las mathe'u chung gnyis mche ba lta bu kha 'gram du bzhag la /
NK020(wa)006:155: khu tshur gnyis dku g.yon du mnan la /
NK020(wa)006:158: rdo rje bsgyings tshul gyis 'dud pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:164: rdo rje khu tshur kha nas dbyung ba'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:167: rdo rje gar bskor ba'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:169: mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi la /
NK020(wa)006:170: rdo rje khu tshur gyis bdug pa dang 'thor ba dang bskor ba dang byug pa ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)006:176: khu tshur las g.yas pa'i mdzub mo dang g.yon pa'i mathe'u chung bcing la /
NK020(wa)006:182: mdzub gnyis gdu bu ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)006:185: rgyab gnyis mnyam ste mnan pa'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)006:187: d+h+ri ta r+aash+t+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:188: g.yas pa'i khu tshur gyi steng du g.yon pa'i khu tshur nang bstan sgreng ba yul 'khor srung /
NK020(wa)006:189: bi r+au d+ha k+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:190: g.yas pa'i khu tshur las gung mdzub sgrang ba 'phags skyes po /
NK020(wa)006:191: bi r+au p+aa k+sh+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:192: rdo rje phyi bsdams las mdzub mo phyung ba mig mi bzang /
NK020(wa)006:193: bee sh+ra wa n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:194: rdo rje phyi bsdams las mathe'u sgreng ba rnam sras /
NK020(wa)006:196: mig steng du phyogs shing thal mo khong stong du sbyar ba ni tshangs pa /
NK020(wa)006:198: lag gnyis kyi mathe'u chung mthe bong gis mnan cing
NK020(wa)006:199: sor mo lhag ma gsum sgrengs te g.yon snying ga
NK020(wa)006:200: dang g.yas dkur bzhag pa ni dbang po /
NK020(wa)006:202: lag gnyis khu tshur las gung mo sgreng ba'i tshigs
NK020(wa)006:203: gsum par mdzub rtse sbyar ba g.yas snying ga dang
NK020(wa)006:204: g.yon dkur bzhag pa ni me lha /
NK020(wa)006:205: kha ya m+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:206: rdo rje nang bsdams las srin lag gnyis brkyang ba ni gshin rje /
NK020(wa)006:207: nee tri t+ya ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:208: lag gnyis khu tshur las gung mdzub gnyis brkyang ba
NK020(wa)006:209: g.yas snying ga dang g.yon dkur bzhag pa ni srin
NK020(wa)006:210: po / wa ru n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:211: khu tshur gnyis kyi mtheb mdzub zhags mig gi tshul
NK020(wa)006:212: du sbyar ba snying gar bzhag pa ni chu lha
NK020(wa)006:214: sngar me lha'i phyag rgya ltar bcas pa las g.yon
NK020(wa)006:215: snying ga dang g.yas dkur bzhag pa ni rlung lhakha
NK020(wa)006:216: / ku be r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:217: rdo rje nang bsdams las mathe'u chung gshibs nas brkyang
NK020(wa)006:218: ba de srin lag brkyang zhing rtse sbyar ba'i nang
NK020(wa)006:219: du bcug pa ni gnod sbyin /
NK020(wa)006:221: rdo rje nang bsdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang pa'i
NK020(wa)006:222: sen mo la mdzub mo gnyis reg cing mthe bong
NK020(wa)006:223: gnyis so so'i phyogs kyi gung mo la sbyar ba
NK020(wa)006:224: ni dbang ldan / s+aur+y+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:226: nyi ma dang zla ba gnyis ni tshangs paka dang 'dra'o //
NK020(wa)006:227: pri thi w+ai b+h+ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:229: a su re b+h+ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:230: mig mthur du blta zhing lag gnyis thal mo khong
NK020(wa)006:231: stong du sbyar ba las mthe bong gnyis nang du
NK020(wa)006:232: bcug la thal mo'i rtse mo mthur du bstan pa
NK020(wa)006:235: lha min gsum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK020(wa)006:237: de wa swam swam ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:238: thal mo khong stong las gung mo gshibs la bsnol /
NK020(wa)006:239: mdzub mo bkug pa'i steng du mthe bong bzhag pa'i phyag rgyas dbul /
NK020(wa)006:241: re re na ti na n+aa ga li ram phu ta ta ri tsi ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:242: lag gnyis kyi thal mo phyir bstan bkan pa gdengs ka ltar bzung ba'i rgya dang bcas dbul /
NK020(wa)006:244: gra he tsa ri ya pra ba dam dzo te mar ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:245: lag gnyis gcig tu sbyar zhing mthe bong gnyis gshibs te sgreng ba'i rgyas dbul /
NK020(wa)006:247: nak+sha tra da ni rat+na da ni ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:248: gaza'i phyag rgya de nyid las gung mo dang mthe bong gnyis ldog ste sbyar bas dbul /
NK020(wa)006:250: yak+she pra r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)006:251: g.yon pa'i thal mo lte ba'i phyogs su bkan te
NK020(wa)006:252: bzhag pa'i mdzub mo bkug cing g.yas pa'i gung mo
